org.jruby.runtime

Class CompiledBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruby.runtime.BlockBody
      • org.jruby.runtime.ContextAwareBlockBody
        • org.jruby.runtime.CompiledBlock
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompiledBlockLight

    public class CompiledBlock
extends ContextAwareBlockBody
    A Block implemented using a Java-based BlockCallback implementation rather than with an ICallable. For lightweight block logic within Java code.
